Disabling IMAP REFERRALS via config option &quot;proxyd_disable_mailbox_referrals&quot;

Hi,
the attached patch contains a configuration option &quot;proxyd_disable_mailbox_referrals&quot; to disable IMAP REFERRALS
on the frontend servers in a murder.

I think this is useful for some scenarios, e.g. when backend server are behind a firewall. 
Please consider this for inclusion in the next version.

Thanks,
Frank</thetext>
